[I] An ISO/IEC 23008-12:2017 HEIF and AVIF file format decoder and encoder

[T] HEIF and AVIF are new image file formats employing HEVC (h.265) or AV1
[T] image coding, respectively, for the best compression ratios currently
[T] possible.

